# Sample project with k8s
https://kubernetes.github.io/ingress-nginx/deploy/#quick-start

## deploy the ingress controller with the following command

```bash
helm upgrade --install ingress-nginx ingress-nginx \
  --repo https://kubernetes.github.io/ingress-nginx \
  --namespace ingress-nginx --create-namespace
```

```bash
helm uninstall ingress-nginx -n ingress-nginx
```


## Add secrets

```bash
kubectl create secret generic pgpassword --from-literal PGPASSWORD=qwert
```

## To start project in development mode with kubernetes cluster

```bash
skaffold dev
```


